OL,10,GHow do you scare someone safely? How
OL,11,Gdo you build terrifying interactions
OL,12,Gthat are still inviting to try? We've
OL,13,Gbeen making novel interactive props
OL,14,Gusing a wide array of technology,
OL,15,Guncovering a design language for
OL,16,Gspooky interaction that has also
OL,17,Ghighlighted how easy it is to make
OL,18,Gsomething unintentionally funny, or
OL,19,Gtoo difficult to understand, or too
OL,20,Gfrightening to have a go, or too
